**Last updated: 22/11/2025 **

Instant QR Scanner (“the App”) respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how the App handles user data.

---

## **1. No Data Collection**

The App **does not collect, store, share, or transmit any personal data** from users.
All QR and barcode scans are processed **locally on your device only**.

---

## **2. Camera Access**

The App requires access to your device’s **camera** solely for the purpose of scanning QR codes and barcodes.
No camera images or videos are recorded, saved, or sent to any server.

---

## **3. No Internet Connection Required**

The App works **offline**.
Your scans and activities remain private and never leave your device.

---

## **4. Third-Party Services**

The App uses **Google Play Services Code Scanner API** for improved scanning performance.
This API may perform basic checks for code recognition but **does not collect personal information**.

---

## **5. Children’s Privacy**

The App does not collect any data and is safe for all ages, including children.

---

## **6. Changes to This Policy**

We may update this Privacy Policy if necessary. You will be notified within the app if any changes occur.

---

## **7. Contact**

If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact:

**Email:** nexrcodeinnovations@gmail.com
**App Name:** Instant QR Scanner

---
